Dialogs.Dialog: You can't do it like a model, right?
Nice to meet you, photographer. Fufu.
Well, I'll do my best too.
If you take a strange picture, it's bad, right?
What kind of photo will it be today? I'm looking forward to it.
Well, it's been a long time before I knew it.
Let's finish this time. The continuation is coming again.
Yeah, how much do you do?
Oh, it's enough to shoot this much.
Fufu, have you taken a lot of pictures?
Sorry. Take it like this again.
Oh. I was crazy about it today.
Isn't it about to end? I think you are getting tired too.
……So be. Then, is it the end?
Ah... I'm sorry, I just forgot about myself.
Oh, that's right. I may have taken a little too much.
You were doing your best. Did it work?
I wonder if that will be fun later.
All right. I took a lot of pictures.
Oh, sorry. I've been shooting all the time.
Hey, do you realize I'm tired?
I'm sorry, I'm a little tired.
I see... Well then, let's do it so far.
Hmm, I'm a little nervous. sorry.
Let's go more comfortably next time.
Fufu, maybe I need more practice?
Pictures are good, but I also want to talk.
That's right... Do you refrain from doing so?
Camera, camera... Your girlfriend isn't a camera, isn't it?
I'm a little lonely because I can't talk if I just shoot.
I don't like it any more. You know?
Uh... I think I got too sick.
I hope you take a beautiful picture.
n/a. Nice to meet you, photographer.
If your heart is in focus, you can take beautiful pictures, right? Nante.
I want you to take a different facial expression than usual.
I hope it will be a nice photo.
It's fun to organize your photos.
Let's take a lot of pictures of them.
Another one will increase your memories. I'm looking forward to it.
In this way, memories will increase one by one.
Memories will remain with the photos.
I want more memories with you.
Don't forget about this moment today.
Do you want to bother me?
I'm still a little embarrassed. Does it look good?
Take it as beautifully as possible.
I'm looking forward to what kind of photo it will be.
It's nice to see more photos.
Let's fill up the memories with me.
Let's make an important memory only for two people.
I will never forget today. you too?
It's nice to have more memories little by little.
Let's make a lot of fun memories from now on.
Please stop because it's a request.
Here and there, I'm not getting along.
It may be embarrassing to see it through the viewfinder.
You don't have to focus too much...
It's more embarrassing to be able to take pictures than I expected.
I don't know what kind of face I should have...
Oh, please say it properly when you shoot.
I'm tired of keeping my eyes open all the time.
Ah! Maybe I was closing my eyes now.
I'm getting used to taking pictures.
A good photographer will not miss a photo opportunity.
I hope I can take good pictures.
Let's do our best for ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲!
Let's have a little adventure today.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ I'm getting used to it.
This kind of angle ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is not bad either.
If ● is not firm, do not make ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ nervous.
I wonder how to take a beautiful picture.
I hope you can take it properly...
It's a special memorial, so I have to do my best.
It's okay if you take a calm shot... Maybe.
I didn't think it would be so nervous to shoot...
Phew. Is it a little good?
I feel really good right now ▼
If it's strange, tell me right away, right?
I wonder why... I don't feel like it.
Do I have to shoot now?
No... did you see it? You can't see it, right?
That is... I wonder if it's a problem.
Even if you see it so much... I'm in trouble.
You shouldn't just look at strange things.
Are you only interested in that kind of thing?
Hey... I feel a naughty look?
Hey! If it was just like that, I would n’t let you shoot anymore.
I don't know what to do anymore.
Hey... are you just looking at your back?
Well... I can't help but be worried.
Are you trying to take a weird photo?
Eh !? No... I'm a mischievous child.
...... I'm grinning. You haven't taken it right now, right?
Shall we stop taking pictures anymore?
There are some pictures that I don't want to be taken.
You took a weird photo right now, right? I can't.
